column1: Includes CPI-trim, CPI-median, and CPI-common as well as other “core” inflation measures.

column2: Total CPI, Percentage Change over 1 year ago (unadjusted)
column3: Total CPI, Percentage Change over 1 year ago (unadjusted)

column2: CPIX, Percentage Change over 1 year ago (unadjusted)
column3: The CPI excluding eight of the most volatile components (fruit, vegetables, gasoline, fuel oil, natural gas, mortgage interest, inter-city transportation and tobacco products) as well as the effect of changes in indirect taxes on the remaining components.

column2: CPI-XFET, Percentage Change over 1 year ago (unadjusted)
column3: The CPI excluding food, energy and the effect of changes in indirect taxes.

column2: CPIW, Percentage Change over 1 year ago (unadjusted)
column3: CPIW adjusts each CPI basket weight by a factor that is inversely proportional to the component's variability and is adjusted to exclude the effect of changes in indirect taxes.
